      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Linear elastic material model appropriate for sub-yield loading regime; contact formulation validated against known analytical solutions.",
      "rationale": "The compression-bending regime for F1717 testing is predominantly elastic at loads below yield force. Linear elastic titanium alloy properties (E=114 GPa, nu=0.34) are well-established. Frictional contact (mu=0.2) applied at screw-rod interface consistent with literature."
    },
