      "acceptanceCriteria": "Test conditions must span clinically relevant load magnitudes and at least two load configurations to establish model generalizability.",
      "rationale": "Only a single static compression-bending load configuration was tested per ASTM F1717. No dynamic, torsional, or varied offset conditions were included. The model has not been validated across the range of in vivo loading scenarios relevant to the COU. This factor falls significantly below the required level, representing a critical gap in the validation evidence base."
    },
    {
