      "rationale": "All three QoIs met acceptance criteria across all three modeling teams. E/uval ranged from 0.31 to 1.44. Maximum percent difference was 7.2% for force at 40 mm displacement. Quantitative agreement is strong for the tested condition."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
