    "rationale": "The credibility assessment team determined that the FEA modeling framework demonstrates High assurance for the COU. Quantitative validation metrics (E/uval, percent difference) met all acceptance criteria across three independent modeling teams and two laboratories. The overall body of evidence is considered sufficient to support regulatory use of the FEA predictions. The single-condition limitation for Test conditions was noted but deemed acceptable given the strong quantitative agreement observed.",
